summary: Adds 5 drag queens to the temples of skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
Adds 5 new followers to the temples of skyrim.

Nellie the archer: Located in the Temple of Mara in Riften.

Johan the mage: Located in the Temple of the Divines in Solitude.

Rosie the warrior: Located in the Temple of Kynareth in Whiterun.

Rebbeca the Shield: Located in the Temple of Dibella in Markarth.

Kazumi the assassin: Located in the Temple of Talos in Windhelm.

Requires Apachii hair http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?

Recommend a mod that makes the male faces look younger.
author: Jackdack
